      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready to hit the road in a car that's full of character and ready for its next adventure! This vehicle is in fair condition and has been a reliable companion, showing some honest signs of use that come with a life well-lived. It's a fantastic, budget-friendly option for anyone looking for a functional ride that still has plenty of miles left to give. With a little bit of care, this car will continue to be a dependable choice for your daily commutes!",
      "price": 20000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
