    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair overall condition. It is currently in running order and can be driven, but it shows clear signs of its age and mileage. The engine starts and runs, though it may require a tune-up soon, and the transmission shifts through all gears but is not as crisp as a newer model. Externally, there are several noticeable scratches, minor dents, and some paint fading on the hood and roof. Inside, the upholstery shows significant wear and a few stains, though the cabin remains functional. This car would be a solid choice for someone looking for an affordable daily driver or a base for a restoration project, provided they are prepared to invest in some upcoming maintenance and cosmetic repairs.",
      "price": 19500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 43
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold strictly as-is. It currently has a non-running engine due to a failed head gasket and requires a complete transmission overhaul. The exterior shows significant rust on the wheel wells and doors, while the interior has heavy wear and several tears in the seats. This would be an ideal project for a mechanic or a valuable source for spare parts, but it will need to be towed from the lot.",
      "price": 3800.0,
